<div class="comment"><div class="commtext c00">It&#x27;s a non-deterministic language model, shouldn&#x27;t we expect mediocre performance in math? It seems like the wrong tool for the job...</div><div class="reply"><p><font size="1"><u><a href="reply?id=44368862&amp;goto=item%3Fid%3D44366494%2344368862" rel="nofollow">reply</a></u></font></div></div></td></tr>
</table></td></tr><tr class="athing comtr" id="44369121"><td><table border="0">  <tr>    <td class='ind' indent='2'><img src="s.gif" height="1" width="80"></td><td valign="top" class="votelinks">
