<div class="comment"><div class="commtext c00">Assuming decent data, it won&#x27;t be stochastic sampling for many math operations&#x2F;input combinations. When people suggest LLMs with tokenization could learn math, they aren&#x27;t suggesting a small undertrained model trained on crappy data.</div><div class="reply"><p><font size="1"><u><a href="reply?id=44371710&amp;goto=item%3Fid%3D44366494%2344371710" rel="nofollow">reply</a></u></font></div></div></td></tr>
