<div class="comment"><div class="commtext c00">And even on open LLMs, GPU instability can cause non-determinism. For performance reasons, determinism is seldom guaranteed in LLMs in general.</div><div class="reply"><p><font size="1"><u><a href="reply?id=44370022&amp;goto=item%3Fid%3D44366494%2344370022" rel="nofollow">reply</a></u></font></div></div></td></tr>
