<div class="comment"><div class="commtext c00">Deterministic is a special case of not-necessarily-deterministic.</div><div class="reply"><p><font size="1"><u><a href="reply?id=44368958&amp;goto=item%3Fid%3D44366494%2344368958" rel="nofollow">reply</a></u></font></div></div></td></tr>
