<div class="comment"><div class="commtext c00">A random number generator is guaranteed to produce a correct solution to any problem, but runtime usually does not meet usability standards.<p>Also, solution testing is mandatory. Luckily, you can ask an RNG for that, too, as long as you have tests for the testers already written.</div><div class="reply"><p><font size="1"><u><a href="reply?id=44367856&amp;goto=item%3Fid%3D44366494%2344367856" rel="nofollow">reply</a></u></font></div></div></td></tr>
